    "description": "Double your main protein. This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. You'll pan-fry chicken breast till golden before smothering it in a honey and ginger buffalo-style sauce. Serve with rice and a crunchy carrot and edamame slaw. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
